---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - MINDMUSH">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-[#0a0a0a]">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
      <nav class="mb-16">
        <a href="/" class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.25em] text-white hover:text-white/70 transition-colors">
          MINDMUSH
        </a>
      </nav>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-4">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/40 mb-16">Last Updated: January 15, 2025</p>

      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-16 leading-relaxed">
        MINDMUSH LLC, based in Delaware, United States, is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share your information when you use our mobile games and services. By using our games, you agree to the collection and use of information as outlined below.
      </p>

      <section class="space-y-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4">When you use our mobile games and services, we may collect the following types of information:</p>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">a. Non-Personal Information</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4">We collect non-personal information, including:</p>
          <ul class="text-white/70 list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Device information (e.g., type, operating system, IP address).</li>
            <li>Game usage data (e.g., levels completed, in-game purchases).</li>
            <li>General user behavior and interaction within the game.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-white/70">This information is used to improve our services and enhance your gaming experience.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">2. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4">We use third-party services to improve your experience and facilitate key features within our games:</p>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">a. App Stores</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4">For in-app purchases, we use Apple App Store and Google Play Store. These platforms process transactions and manage payment information.</p>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">b. AppLovin</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4">We utilize AppLovin for ad mediation to deliver personalized ads within the game.</p>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">c. Tapjoy</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70">We use Tapjoy for offerwalls, which provide opportunities to earn in-game rewards through interacting with ads.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4">We use the information we collect to:</p>
          <ul class="text-white/70 list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Provide and maintain our games and services.</li>
            <li>Personalize in-game content and advertisements.</li>
            <li>Improve game performance and user experience.</li>
            <li>Process in-app purchases through app stores.</li>
            <li>Offer rewards through Tapjoy's offerwalls.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">4. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
          <p class="text-white/70">We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. However, we may share non-personal information with third-party service providers like AppLovin, Tapjoy, and app stores to facilitate ads, game performance analytics, and in-app purchases.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">5. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="text-white/70">We implement appropriate measures to protect the information we collect. However, no system is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security of your data.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">6. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-white/70">Our services are not intended for children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe that a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us, and we will take steps to remove the data.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">7. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-white/70">Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your data, such as the right to access, correct, or delete your information. If you wish to exercise these rights, please contact us at the address provided below.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-white/70">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices. Significant updates will be posted within the game or on our website. Please check this policy periodically for updates.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">9. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-6">If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at:</p>

          <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-8 space-y-1">
            <p class="text-white font-semibold">MINDMUSH LLC</p>
            <p class="text-white/70">1111B S Governors Ave STE 49061</p>
            <p class="text-white/70">Dover, DE 19904 US</p>
            <p class="text-white/70">Phone: +1 (332) 290-9021</p>
            <p class="text-white/70">Email: <a href="mailto:contact@mindmush.com" class="text-white hover:text-white/70 transition-colors">contact@mindmush.com</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/[0.03] rounded-lg p-6 mt-12">
          <p class="text-white/70 font-medium">By using our games and services, you agree to this Privacy Policy.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
